com.pedroalmir.athena.core.component
Interface AthenaBundle

All Superinterfaces:
PersistentEntity, java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
GenericConverter, GenericModule
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractBundle, FromCSVConverter, FuzzyModule, NSGAIIModule, ToCSVConverter
public interface AthenaBundle
extends PersistentEntity

This interface was designed to represent any component to be integrated into the tool. Thus we can work in a general way, for example, in the case of links. A link may be a link from one module to another module or the connection between a module and a converter. Initially this interface has no methods defined.

Since:
25/06/2013
Author:
Pedro Almir
